The '''Arra Desert''' was a vast [[Desert/Legends|desert]] located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sorrus]]. It was formed in [[53 BBY/Legends|53 BBY]] when the government dammed up a nearby [[Water/Legends|water]] source, draining the area of water for ten years.

